title: A Room With a View (1985)
description:
Be sure to read the comments file.

I first saw this movie about the time it came out.
My reaction to it has not been at all what the people writing the comments say.
I guess I'm not nearly as well versed in literature and cinema as they seem to be. I enjoy the movie, but I'm not as enthusiastic as all that.

There are embedded subtitles, so I do not include the usual subtitle file.
